.SH Name
.SP 5 5
glance - Quick description of the room or an object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
glance
glance at <thing>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Glance is to be used to look at something briefly without being noticed
and without going through the long description.
